  "title": "General Manager",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p>1. Responsible for the comprehensive management planning, market development, customer maintenance, routeexpansion, and carrying out shipping agency business in the Shipping & Operations department under the guidanceof the board of directors and the general manager.</p><p>2. Responsible for and guiding the Chartering Department in contract negotiations, cargo arrangements on ownvessel, assigning of vessel operators, reviewing operational expenses etc.</p><p>3. Responsible for coordinating the cargo arrangements and voyage task assignments with Specialized team inChina Headquarter.</p><p>4. Responsible for communicating with the Shipping & Marketing Management Division in Headquarter, andcooperating with the headquarters in regional market development, marketing promotion, customer maintenance.and collecting marketing information etc.</p><p>5. Responsible for communicating with the fleet teams regarding negotiations, execution of shipping agencybusiness agreements within the region, and developing agency business market.</p><p>6. Responsible for developing end-to-end projects within the region, such as: pulp logistics, automobile logisticsand regional inland transportation projects.</p><p>7. Responsible for managing the company's various country representative offices and guiding the representativesin market development, customer maintenance, contract negotiations, vessel chartering etc.</p><p>8. Responsible for new employee training, management, and job advancement, managing day to day work for thestaffs in Shipping Operations Department etc.</p><p>9. Responsible for the relevant reports within the department.</p><p>10. Other tasks assigned by management.</p>",
