    "description": "<p>COSCO SHIPPING Specialized Carriers (Southeast Asia) Pte.Ltd.is a newly-established indirect wholly-owned subsidiary of COSCO SHIPPING Specialized Carriers Co., Ltd. (<a href=\"http://en.spe.coscoshipping.com/\">http://en.spe.coscoshipping.com/</a>), listed on the Shanghai Stock Exchange (Stock Code: 600428) and is ultimately state-owned by China COSCO SHIPPING Corporation Limited.</p>\n<p>The principal activities of COSCO SHIPPING Specialized Carriers (Southeast Asia) Pte.Ltd. are shipping and shipping related activities such as shipping agent, freight agent, freight forwarder, transit agent, transport operator, shipbroker, stevedore, and all trading relating to shipments by road, water and air, maritime representation, import and export, purchase and sale and distribution of goods.</p>",
